title: About
text:
This is a personal website I am making for STAT 37815: Practical R Programming with Extensions with Dr. McShane.
I plan on publishing my resume, programming projects, and other interests on this website.

title: Home Page
text: I’m a second-year Master’s student at UChicago studying Computational and Applied Mathematics. Prior to UChicago, I attended Southern Methodist University from 2019-2023, where I received a BBA in Finance and a minor in Computer Science. You can view my resume here
